				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Charm. 
<br />

<br />
CH has been lowered in effectiveness over the years with the way encounters are designed.
<br />

<br />
Charm however, can make any encounter easier if charmed creatures are available. Nothing beats the DPS a hasted charmed critter can do. For example, Plane of Storms. Even if everyone has gimp gear, you can kill one of the named with enough charmed pets. Just bring as many druids/enchanters as you can, and do mass charm zerg.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">The pet defense upgrades are a very nice start, however the balancing is not over. There are still issues with how much DPS pets are capable of on raid mobs, and there are still issues in how much the Mage class is desired in raids for their damage in a raid enviorment.</span>
<br />
